'' 'Fondation Eye Care Foundation' '' ('' ECF '') ni umuryango mpuzamahanga utabara imbabare ukorera mu bihugu birenga 20 byo muri [[Aziya]]<ref>[https://guardian.ng/news/africas-first-rotary-eye-hospital-nearing-completion-in-lagos/ Africa's Rumah Sakit Mata Rotary pertama hampir selesai di Lagos] The Guardian.ng (6 Sep 2017). Diakses pada 04 Mei 2018.</ref><ref>[https://www.vanguardngr.com/2018/04/free-health-mission-8-month-old-aged-regain-sight/ 8-month old , tua, penglihatan kembali] VanGuardngr.com (18 April 2018). Diakses pada 05 Mei 2018.</ref>

ECF yashinzwe igihe '' Eyecare Worldwide '' na '' Abaganga b'amaso ya Mekong '' yahujwe [[2008]]. <ref>[https://beta.volkskrant.nl/economie/instellingen-ooghulp-slaan-handen-ineen~b326b9b2 / Instellingen ooghulp slaan handen ineen] Volkskrant.nl (25 Juli 2008). Diakses pada 05 Mei 2018.</ref> Amashyirahamwe yombi yasangiye intego kandi akorana nkuko umusingi uriho wagaragaye ko ari mwiza. [[CEO]] wa ECF ni [[Björn Stenvers]].

== Amateka ==
Eyecare Worldwide (1984) yashinzwe na [[] umuganga] [[ijisho] umuganga] [w’Ubuholandi]] wagize ingaruka ku kibazo cy’abantu benshi bahumye. Bashobora gukira cyangwa no gukumirwa. Abaganga b'amaso ya Mekong (1993) yashinzwe n’umuhanga mu binyabuzima w’Ubuholandi nyuma yo kuba muri Tayilande [Tayilande | Tayilande] akora ubushakashatsi [[]].

Eye Foundation ishyigikira imishinga yo muri [[Kambodiya]], [[Lawosi‎]], [[Nepali‎]], [[Tanzaniya]][na] [[Viyetinamu‎]] mu rwego rwo gukumira no gukiza ubumuga bwo kutabona no kutabona. Kwiyegurira Imana bifasha kandi abantu badashoboye kwitabwaho neza kandi badashobora kwivuza amaso nkamaso cyangwa kubaga amaso.

Fondation Eye Care ifite ibiro n'ibitaro muri Himalaya, [[Nepali‎]], Amajyepfo yAmajyepfo ya Aziya ([[Viyetinamu‎]]),<ref>[https://www.sc.com/global/av/eye-care-programme.pdf Standard Chartered memperluas program perawatan mata ke tambahan 2,2 juta orang di [[Viyetinamu‎]]]</ref> [[Kambodiya]], [[Lawosi‎]]) na [[Afurika]] ([[Tanzaniya]], [[Rwanda]]).<ref>[https://www.northwestsignal.net/news/article_a9e07fdf-5218-5517-befd-d90dd5f229a8.html Local Lions Club belajar tentang Eye Care Foundation] Northwest Signal.net]</ref> [[Toine van Peperstraten]] adalah Ambassador untuk Eye Care Foundation.<ref>[https://nederlandsmedianieuws.nl/TV-en-Video/tv-en-video-nieuws/Toine-van-Peperstraten-zet-zich-in-voor-Eye-Care-Foundation/ ]</ref>
== Igihugu gikora ==

=== [[Tanzaniya]] ===
ECF ishyigikira ikigo nderabuzima cya gikirisitu cya Kilimanjaro (KCMC) ishami ryubuzima bwamaso <ref>[https://www.kcmc.ac.tz/Services/eye.php kcmc.ac.tz]</ref> kuva [2009]] kandi ifite ibiro muri [[Tanzaniya]] kuva [[2018]]. <ref>[https://www.iapb.org/about/news/eye-care-foundation-activities-in- tanzania/ ]</ref>

=== [[Kambodiya]]===
Fondasiyo yatanze inkunga yo kwita kumaso muri [[Kambodiya]]kuva 1997, kugirango ifashe abatishoboye mubukungu n'imibereho myiza. ECF igamije kubaka umuyoboro uhamye wo kwita kumaso no gutanga ubuvuzi buhendutse bushyira amashami meza yo kwita kumaso mubitaro byaho. ubufatanye na serivisi z'ubuzima zo mu karere muri leta za Ratanakiri, Mondulkiri, Kratie, Svay Rieng, Tbong Khmum, Preah Vihear, Oddar Meanchey na Pailin. ECF yatangije serivisi zita kumaso kumatsinda nkabantu bake, ababana nubumuga, nabagore nabana.<ref>[https://www.ccc-cambodia.org/en/ngodb/ngo-information/325 ccc-cambodia.org ]</ref>

=== [[Lawosi‎]]===
ECF yasuye [[Lawosi‎]] ku nshuro ya mbere mu 2007, itangiza imishinga muri leta ya Xieng Khouang na Houa Phanh mu mwaka wa 2011. Hatanzwe ubufasha muri utwo turere kugira ngo hongerwe ireme no kuvura amaso. Muri 2018, hafunguwe ibiro by’ubuhinzi muri [[Lawosi‎]]. Inzobere ebyiri z’amaso zarangije gutura kwa Othalmology maze batangira imirimo yabo ku mishinga yo muri leta za Houaphan na Saysomboun. Kuri Sayomboun, hashyizweho ishami rishya ryita kumaso kandi ritegurwa. Umwaka- raporo-2016.pdf | url-status = live}} </ref>

=== [[Nepali‎]] ===
ECF ishyigikira ibitaro bibiri bikomeye muri [[Nepali‎]]; kuri Match na Pokhara. ECF ishyigikira gahunda zubuzima bwamaso muri Gandaki, Dhaulagiri, Imikino, Gorkha na Karnali. Ibiro bya [[Nepali‎]]byafunguwe mu 1988. <ref> {{Tanga urubuga | umutwe = Ibitaro by'amaso bya Himalaya | url = http: //heh.org.np/ | kwinjira-itariki = 2021-05-06 | ururimi = en-US}} </ref>

=== [[Viyetinamu‎]]===
ECF yagiye itera inkunga amaso muri [[Viyetinamu‎]]kuva mu 1993. Mbere, fondasiyo yagize uruhare mu gutegura ingando z’amaso ziyobowe n’ubuvuzi bw’amaso n’abaforomo bo mu Buholandi, zifasha kuvura abarwayi benshi ba cataracte bishoboka. ECF yashyizeho Centre 2 za Vision muri Vinh Long na Dong Thap, ku nkunga y'abaterankunga, kandi yongeraho 16 hamwe na Vision Centre hamwe n’inkunga yihariye mu karere ka Mekong Delta. Ibiro bya [[Viyetinamu‎]]muri Ho Chi City Minh byafunguwe muri 2008.

